venue.name: Kedai Makanan Ah Jui Chaah Johor
Kedai Makanan Ah Jui Chaah Johor

tip.text: Steam fish...vinegar pork knuckle...braised pork belly...
Variety of warm bread...the curry bun is good. Ample seating...friendly staff...very cosy.
Of the 4 hock Chew mee that I had tried in Yong Peng..this is my favourite.

venue.name: Restoran Sate Rahmad, Pekan Parit Yaani

tip.text: Our fantastic hosts Ludo and Pedro....thank you very much ....gracias...
Charcoal oven baked lamb n piglet legs...yummy.
Cheese crab...sweet potatoes leaves...generous amount of sauce with the crab n loaf of massimo bread to dip into the sauce...

venue.name: Blk 216 Bedok North Street 1 Hawker & Food Centre

tip.text: I am back to try their Nasi lemak ...yes..it is good...
Roasted pork..char siew..Roasted duck...choi sum...white coffee...braised dark soya sauce tofu n egg
